ipura, India.\n|-\n|India\n|26 March 2017\n|Bangladesh High Commission,  Agartala,Tripura, India.\n|-\n|India\n|4 January 2017\n|All India Women's Congress, Kolkata.\n|-\n|India\n|2 January 2017\n|\"Kolpotoru Mela\"Razarhat, Kolkata.\n|-\n|India\n|1 January 2017\n|National Poetry Festival & Newtown Book Fair, Kolkata.\n|-\n|India\n|27 March 2016\n|Birla Academy of Arts & Culture, Kolkata\n|-\n|India\n|26 March 2016\n|Rabindra Sadan, Kolkata\n|-\n|Sri Lanka\n|17 & 26 March 2011\n|High Commission Hall Room, Bangladesh High Commission, Sri Lanka.\n|-\n| India\n|9-16 March 1989\n|Open Stage, Kolkata University Auditorium, Kolkata City\n\nOpen Stage, Kollyani University\n|}\n\n==Awards==\n{{Excessive citations|section|date=April 2020}}\n[[File:Kamal Ahmed receives FOBANA Award.jpg|Ahmed received FOBANA Award (2017)|thumb]]\n[[File:Dhirendranath Dutta Award.jpg|thumb|Ahmed with his \"Beer Shaheed Dhirendranath Dutta Award\"]]\n# SAARC Cultural Society Award (2010) <ref>{{Cite news|last=|first=|url=http://kamalahmedsinger.com/saarc-cultural-society-award/|title=SAARC Cultural Society Award|date=|work=|access-date=|via=}}</ref>\n#Bangabandhu Research Foundation Podok (2015).''<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thedailysangbad.com/entertainment/2016/04/01/58919|title=\u09b8\u0982\u0997\u09c0\u09a4\u09c7 \u0985\u09ac\u09a6\u09be\u09a8\u09c7\u09b0 \u099c\u09a8\u09cd\u09af \u09aa\u09a6\u0995 \u09aa\u09c7\u09b2\u09c7\u09a8 \u0995\u09be\u09ae\u09be\u09b2 \u0986\u09b9\u09ae\u09c7\u09a6|accessdate=2016-04-01|publisher=\u09a6\u09c8\u09a8\u09bf\u0995 \u09b8\u0982\u09ac\u09be\u09a6|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020041944/http://www.thedailysangbad.com/entertainment/2016/04/01/58919|archive-date=2016-10-20|url-status=dead}}</ref>''\n# Adwaitia Mallabarman Award (2017), From Maharaja Beerbikram University, India.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.thedailystar.net/arts-entertainment/kamal-ahmed-receives-adwaita-mallabarman-award-1385752|title=Kamal Ahmed receives Adwaita Mallaba