ily Janakantha|language=en|access-date=2020-04-09}}</ref>\n\n== Albums ==\n*Shada Megher Bhela (2007) -Tagore Songs.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://kamalahmedsinger.com/shada-megher-bhela-2007/|title=Sada Megher Bhela|last=|first=|date=|work=|access-date=|via=}}</ref>\n*Nana Ronger Dinguli (2008) -Tagore Songs.\n*Poth Chawatei Ananda (2009) -Tagore Songs.\n*Falguner Dine (2010) -Tagore Songs.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thedailystar.net/news-detail-142833|title=Kamal Ahmed's \"Phalguner Din-e\"| accessdate=2010-06-16 |publisher=The Daily Star}}</ref>\n*Nishshobdo Charane (2011)  -Tagore Songs. (Mixed Album) \n*Godhuli (2012) \u2013 A Tribute to Kishore Kumar.\n*Kan Pete Roi (2013) -Tagore Songs.\n*Bendechhi Amar Pran (2014) -Tagore Songs.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://archive.thedailystar.net/news2014/kamal-ahmeds-bendhechhi-amar-pran-released-27196|title=Kamal Ahmed's \"Bendhechhi Amar Pran\" released'| accessdate=2014-06-06 |publisher=The Daily Star}}</ref>\n*Bhora Thak Smritishudhay (2015) -Tagore Songs.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theindependentbd.com/arcprint/details/10511/2015-08-06|title=Kamal Ahmed releases 8th solo album ahead of Tagore's death anniv| accessdate=2015-08-06 |publisher=The Independent}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.daily-sun.com/post/64703/Kamal-Ahmedrsquos-New-Tagore-Album-ldquoVora-Thak-Smritishudhayrdquo-launched|title=Kamal Ahmed's New Tagore Album \"Vora Thak Smritishudhay\" launched| accessdate=2015-08-06 |publisher=The Daily Sun}}</ref>\n*Oadhora (2016) - Basic Modern Songs.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.observerbd.com/details.php?id=183837|title='Oadhora' by Kamal Ahmed launched - Art & Culture - observerbd.com|website=The Daily Observer|access-date=2019-06-30}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.daily-sun.com/printversion/details/371830|title=Kamal's new album released|website=Daily Sun|language=en|access-date=2019-06-30}}</ref>\n*Gaaner Toree (2016) - Songs of three Poets.\n*Baluka Belay (2016)- A Tribute to Hemanta Mukherji\n*Nidrahara Rater Gan ( 2016)  -Tagore Songs.\n*Durer Bondhu (2016) -Tagore Songs.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thedailystar.net/arts-entertainment/music/kamal-ahmeds-%E2%80%9Cdurer-bondhu%E2%80%9D-releases-today-1265113|title=Kamal Ahmed's \"Durer Bondhu\" releases today| accessdate= |publisher=The Daily Star}}</ref>\n*Mohakabyer Kobi ( 2016) - In India - A Tribute to Father of the Nation Bangabandhu Sheikh Mujibur Rahman.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theindependentbd.com/post/55905|title=Kamal Ahmed's homage to Bangabandhu thru 'Mohakabyer Kobi' | accessdate=2016-08-15 |publisher=The Independent}}</ref>\n*Ekusher Shwaralipi (2019) \u2013 Songs of Shaheed & International Mother Language Day<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thedailystar.net/arts-entertainment/music/news/we-have-move-forward-our-heritage-kamal-ahmed-1704907|title=\"We have to move forward, but with our heritage\" \u2013 Kamal Ahmed|date=2019-02-21|website=The Daily Star|language=en|access-date=2019-06-30}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thedailystar.net/arts-entertainment/music/singer-kamal-ahmed-releases-16th-solo-album-1697854|title=Kamal Ahmed releases 16th solo album|date=2019-02-06|website=The Daily Star|language=en|access-date=2019-06-30}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://m.thedailynewnation.com/news/205532|title=Kamal Ahmed\u00e2\u20ac\u2122s new solo album released|website=m.thedailynewnation.com|access-date=2019-06-30}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.daily-sun.com/printversion/details/368739|title=Kamal Ahmed's 16th Solo Album released|website=Daily Sun|language=en|access-date=2019-07-16}}</ref>\n*Neel Shomudro (2020) \u2013 Romantic Duet Modern.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thedailystar.net/arts-entertainment/news/kamal-ahmeds-neel-shomudro-released-1849060|title=Kamal Ahmed\u2019s \u2018Neel Shomudro\u2019 released|date=2020-01-04|website=The Daily Star|language=en|access-date=2020-04-06}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.daily-sun.com/printversion/details/451237/Kam