09cd\u09af\u09c7\u09b0-\u0995\u09ac\u09bf\u2019|title=\u09b6\u09bf\u09b2\u09cd\u09aa\u09c0 \u0995\u09be\u09ae\u09be\u09b2 \u0986\u09b9\u09ae\u09c7\u09a6\u09c7\u09b0 \u098f\u09cd\u09af\u09be\u09b2\u09ac\u09be\u09ae \u2018\u09ae\u09b9\u09be\u0995\u09be\u09ac\u09cd\u09af\u09c7\u09b0 \u0995\u09ac\u09bf\u2019 {{!}}{{!}} The Daily Janakantha|website=Daily Janakantha|language=en|access-date=2020-04-06}}</ref>\n\n== Documentary film ==\nAhmed has created a documentary film; ''Dhonir Oagropothik'' is a documentary film made to celebrate the diamond jubilee of Bangladesh Betar.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://bangla.thereport24.com/article/81268/index.html|title=\u0995\u09be\u09ae\u09be\u09b2 \u0986\u09b9\u09ae\u09c7\u09a6\u09c7\u09b0 '\u09a7\u09cd\u09ac\u09a8\u09bf\u09b0 \u0985\u0997\u09cd\u09b0\u09aa\u09a5\u09bf\u0995'| accessdate=2015-01-14 |publisher=The Report}}</ref> The planning, research and direction of the film have all been done by Ahmed.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.unitednews24.com/%E0%A6%95%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%AE%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B2-%E0%A6%86%E0%A6%B9%E0%A6%AE%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%A6%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B0-%E0%A6%B6%E0%A7%88%E0%A6%B2%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%AA%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%95-%E0%A6%AF%E0%A7%8B/|title=\u0995\u09be\u09ae\u09be\u09b2 \u0986\u09b9\u09ae\u09c7\u09a6\u09c7\u09b0 \u09b6\u09c8\u09b2\u09cd\u09aa\u09bf\u0995 \u09af\u09cb\u0997\u09cd\u09af\u09a4\u09be\u09b0 \u099b\u09be\u09aa '\u09a7\u09cd\u09ac\u09a8\u09bf\u09b0 \u0985\u0997\u09cd\u09b0\u09aa\u09a5\u09bf\u0995'| accessdate=2015-01-14 |publisher=United News24.com}}</ref>\n\nThe documentary highlights the contribution of Bangladesh Betar to the country and the people during the war of liberation in 1971. is highlighted in the documentary.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.ittefaq.com.bd/print-edition/entertainment/2015/01/17/26343.html|title='\u09a7\u09cd\u09ac\u09a8\u09bf\u09b0 \u0985\u0997\u09cd\u09b0\u09aa\u09a5\u09bf\u0995' \u09a8\u09bf\u09af\u09bc\u09c7 \u0995\u09be\u09ae\u09be\u09b2 \u0986\u09b9\u09ae\u09c7\u09a6| accessdate=2015-01-17 |publisher=The Daily Ittefaq}}</ref>\n\n== Music Videos ==\n1) Bhulite Parina Take \u2013 Modern \n\n2) Bhalobeshe Shakhi - Tagore Song.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://thedailynewnation.com/news/215162?regenerate|title=Music video of Bhalobeshe Sokhi Nibhritey Jotoney|last=Nation|first=The New|website=The New Nation|language=en|access-date=2020-04-06}}</ref>\n\n3) Bhora Thak Smritishudhay \u2013Tagore Song\u00a0\n\n4) Megh Rong \u2013 Borsha Biroho.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thedailystar.net/arts-entertainment/news/kamal-ahmeds-megh-rong-release-june-15-1756009|title=Kamal Ahmed\u2019s \u2018Megh Rong\u2019 to release on June 15|date=2019-06-13|website=The Daily Star|language=en|access-date=2020-04-06}}</ref>\n\n5) Ekush Tumi Lal Potaka - Song of Shaheed and International Mother Language Day.\u00a0\n\n6) Ekush Manei - Song of Shaheed and International Mother Language Day. \n\n7) Poloke Heshe Chole Jao - Modern. <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.daily-sun.com/printversion/details/424892/Kamal-Ahmed\u2019s-new-video-song-released-|title=Kamal Ahmed\u2019s new video song released|website=Daily Sun|language=en|access-date=2020-04-06}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.dailyjanakantha.com/details/article/449027/\u0995\u09be\u09ae\u09be\u09b2-\u0986\u09b9\u09ae\u09c7\u09a6\u09c7\u09b0-\u09b2\u09bf\u09b0\u09bf\u0995\u09cd\u09af\u09be\u09b2-\u09ad\u09bf\u09a1\u09bf\u0993-\u2018\u09aa\u09b2\u0995\u09c7-\u09b9\u09c7\u09b8\u09c7|title=\u0995\u09be\u09ae\u09be\u09b2 \u0986\u09b9\u09ae\u09c7\u09a6\u09c7\u09b0 \u09b2\u09bf\u09b0\u09bf\u0995\u09cd\u09af\u09be\u09b2 \u09ad\u09bf\u09a1\u09bf\u0993 \u2018\u09aa\u09b2\u0995\u09c7 \u09b9\u09c7\u09b8\u09c7 \u099a\u09b2\u09c7 \u09af\u09be\u0993\u2019 {{!}}{{!}} The Daily Janakantha|website=Daily Janakantha|language=en|access-date=2020-04-06}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ittefaq.com.bd/print-edition/entertainment/89835/\u0995\u09be\u09ae\u09be\u09b2-\u0986\u09b9\u09ae\u09c7\u09a6\u09c7\u09b0-\u09aa\u09b2\u0995\u09c7-\u09b9\