114973#sthash.cF3nMZlM.gbpl|title=Kamal Ahmed receives 'FOBANA Award' - Art & Culture - observerbd.com|work=The Daily Observer|access-date=2018-01-26|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.daily-sun.com/printversion/details/279621/Singer-Kamal-receives-FOBANA-Award|title=Singer Kamal receives FOBANA Award- daily sun|last=Sun|first=The Daily|date=|work=Daily Sun|access-date=2018-01-26|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://m.thedailynewnation.com/news/160389|title=Kamal Ahmed receives FOBANA Award in Canada|website=m.thedailynewnation.com|language=en|access-date=2018-01-26}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://samakal.com/sahitto-o-sangskriti/article/1801495/-%E2%80%98%E0%A6%AB%E0%A7%8B%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%BE-%E0%A6%85%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%AF%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%93%E0%A7%9F%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B0%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%A1-%E0%A6%AA%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B2%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%A8-%E0%A6%95%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%AE%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B2-%E0%A6%86%E0%A6%B9%E0%A6%AE%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%A6------|title='\u09ab\u09cb\u09ac\u09be\u09a8\u09be \u0985\u09cd\u09af\u09be\u0993\u09af\u09bc\u09be\u09b0\u09cd\u09a1' \u09aa\u09c7\u09b2\u09c7\u09a8 \u0995\u09be\u09ae\u09be\u09b2 \u0986\u09b9\u09ae\u09c7\u09a6|last=Team|first=Samakal Online|work=\u09b8\u09ae\u0995\u09be\u09b2|access-date=2018-01-26|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://print.thesangbad.net/news/entertaminment/%E0%A6%AB%E0%A7%8B%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%BE+%E0%A6%85%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%AF%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%93%E0%A7%9F%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B0%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%A1+%E0%A6%AA%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B2%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%A8+%E0%A6%95%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%AE%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B2+%E0%A6%86%E0%A6%B9%E0%A6%AE%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%A6-16415/|title=\u09ab\u09cb\u09ac\u09be\u09a8\u09be \u0985\u09cd\u09af\u09be\u0993\u09af\u09bc\u09be\u09b0\u09cd\u09a1 \u09aa\u09c7\u09b2\u09c7\u09a8 \u0995\u09be\u09ae\u09be\u09b2 \u0986\u09b9\u09ae\u09c7\u09a6 {{!}} today.thesangbad.net|last=|first=|date=|website=today.thesangbad.net|language=en|access-date=2018-01-26}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http