54|title=Kamal Ahmed releases 16th solo album|date=2019-02-06|website=The Daily Star|language=en|access-date=2019-06-30}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://m.thedailynewnation.com/news/205532|title=Kamal Ahmed\u00e2\u20ac\u2122s new solo album released|website=m.thedailynewnation.com|access-date=2019-06-30}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.daily-sun.com/printversion/details/368739|title=Kamal Ahmed's 16th Solo Album released|website=Daily Sun|language=en|access-date=2019-07-16}}</ref>\n*Neel Shomudro (2020) \u2013 Romantic Duet Modern.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thedailystar.net/arts-entertainment/news/kamal-ahmeds-neel-shomudro-released-1849060|title=Kamal Ahmed\u2019s \u2018Neel Shomudro\u2019 released|date=2020-01-04|website=The Daily Star|language=en|access-date=2020-04-06}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.daily-sun.com/printversion/details/451237/Kamal-Ahmed\u2019s-17th-audio-album-released|title=Kamal Ahmed\u2019s 17th audio album released|website=Daily Sun|language=en|access-date=2020-04-06}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.dailyjanakantha.com/details/article/471868/\u0995\u09be\u09ae\u09be\u09b2-\u0986\u09b9\u09ae\u09c7\u09a6\u09c7\u09b0-\u09a8\u09a4\u09c1\u09a8-\u098f\u09cd\u09af\u09be\u09b2\u09ac\u09be\u09ae-\u2018\u09a8\u09c0\u09b2-\u09b8\u09ae\u09c1\u09a6\u09cd\u09b0\u2019|title=\u0995\u09be\u09ae\u09be\u09b2 \u0986\u09b9\u09ae\u09c7\u09a6\u09c7\u09b0 \u09a8\u09a4\u09c1\u09a8 \u098f\u09cd\u09af\u09be\u09b2\u09ac\u09be\u09ae \u2018\u09a8\u09c0\u09b2 \u09b8\u09ae\u09c1\u09a6\u09cd\u09b0\u2019 {{!}}{{!}} The Daily Janakantha|website=Daily Janakantha|language=en|access-date=2020-04-06}}</ref>\n*Mohakabyer Kobi ( 2020) - In Bangladesh - A Tribute to Father of The Nation Bangabandhu Sheikh Mujibur Rahman.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thedailystar.net/arts-entertainment/news/kamal-ahmeds-mohakabyer-kobi-celebrates-bangabandhus-birth-centenary-1882624|title=Kamal Ahmed\u2019s \u2018Mohakabyer Kobi\u2019 celebrates Bangabandhu\u2019s birth centenary|date=2020-03-19|website=The Daily Star|language=en|access-date=2020-04-06}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.daily-sun.com/printversion/details/469948/Kamal-Ahmed\u2019s-\u2018Mohakabyer-Kobi\u2019-released|title=Kamal Ahmed\u2019s \u2018Mohakabyer Kobi\u2019 released|website=Daily Sun|language=en|access-date=2020-04-06}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.theindependentbd.com/printversion/details/241470|title=Kamal Ahmed\u2019s \u2018Mahakabyer Kabi\u2019 released|website=Kamal Ahmed\u2019s \u2018Mahakabyer Kabi\u2019 released {{!}} theindependentbd.com|access-date=2020-04-06}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.dailyjanakantha.com/details/article/487821/\u09b6\u09bf\u09b2\u09cd\u09aa\u09c0-\u0995\u09be\u09ae\u09be\u09b2-\u0986\u09b9\u09ae\u09c7\u09a6\u09c7\u09b0-\u098f\u09cd\u09af\u09be\u09b2\u09ac\u09be\u09ae-\u2018\u09ae\u09b9\u09be\u0995\u09be\u09ac\u09cd\u09af\u09c7\u09b0-\u0995\u09ac\u09bf\u2019|title=\u09b6\u09bf\u09b2\u09cd\u09aa\u09c0 \u0995\u09be\u09ae\u09be\u09b2 \u0986\u09b9\u09ae\u09c7\u09a6\u09c7\u09b0 \u098f\u09cd\u09af\u09be\u09b2\u09ac\u09be\u09ae \u2018\u09ae\u09b9\u09be\u0995\u09be\u09ac\u09cd\u09af\u09c7\u09b0 \u0995\u09ac\u09bf\u2019 {{!}}{{!}} The Daily Janakantha|website=Daily Janakantha|language=en|access-date=2020-04-06}}</ref>\n\n== Documentary film ==\nAhmed has created a documentary film; ''Dhonir Oagropothik'' is a documentary film made to celebrate the diamond jubilee of Bangladesh Betar.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://bangla.thereport24.com/article/81268/index.html|title=\u0995\u09be\u09ae\u09be\u09b2 \u0986\u09b9\u09ae\u09c7\u09a6\u09c7\u09b0 '\u09a7\u09cd\u09ac\u09a8\u09bf\u09b0 \u0985\u0997\u09cd\u09b0\u09aa\u09a5\u09bf\u0995'| accessdate=2015-01-14 |publisher=The Report}}</ref> The planning, research and direction of the film have all been done by Ahmed.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.unitednews24.com/%E0%A6%95%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%AE%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B2-%E0%A6%86%E0%A6%B9%E0%A6%AE%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%A6%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B0-%E0%A6%B6%E0%